dct_title_s: Map of New Jersey : compiled from the latest authorities
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. "Entered according to act of Congress, in the year 1850, by Thomas, Cowperthwait & Co." In upper right-hand margin: 13. Includes table of distances of "Routes from Trenton" and population statistics to 1850.
